<content>
    <chapter line="1">Adhikaraṇapaccayakathāvaṇṇanā</chapter>
    <paragraph line="2" number="285"><bold>Vivādādhikaraṇamhā</bold>ti ‘‘adhammaṃ ‘dhammo’ti dīpetī’’tiādinayappavattā aṭṭhārasabhedakaravatthunissitā vivādādhikaraṇamhā.</paragraph>
    <paragraph line="3" number="286"> Upasampannaṃ omasato bhikkhussa pācitti hotīti yojanā.</paragraph>
    <paragraph line="4" number="287"><bold>Anuvādādhikaraṇapaccayā</bold>ti <pageBreak edition="Myanmar" number="2.0440" /><pageBreak edition="Vipassana Research Institut" number="2.0347" /> codanāparanāmadheyyaṃ anuvādādhikaraṇameva paccayo, tasmā, anuvādanādhikaraṇahetūti attho.</paragraph>
    <paragraph line="5" number="289"><bold>‘‘Tathā’’</bold>ti iminā amūlakattaṃ atidisati.</paragraph>
    <paragraph line="6" number="290"><bold>Āpattipaccayā</bold>ti āpattādhikaraṇapaccayā.</paragraph>
    <paragraph line="7" number="293"><bold>Kiccādhikaraṇapaccayā</bold>ti apalokanādicatubbidhakammasaṅkhātakiccādhikaraṇahetu.</paragraph>
    <paragraph line="8" number="294"><bold>Accajantīvā</bold>ti attano laddhiṃ apariccajantī eva.</paragraph>
    <paragraph line="9" number="297"><bold>Pāpikāya diṭṭhiyā</bold> pariccajanatthāya katāya <bold>yāvatatiyakaṃ samanubhāsanāya</bold> taṃ diṭṭhiṃ accajantiyā <bold>tassā</bold> bhikkhuniyā, tassa bhikkhussa ca <bold>accajato</bold> pācitti hotīti yojanā.</paragraph>
    <centered line="10">Iti uttare līnatthapakāsaniyā</centered>
    <centered line="11">Adhikaraṇapaccayakathāvaṇṇanā niṭṭhitā.</centered>
  </content>
